---
title: One-Pot Southwest Beyond Meat® and Cavatappi with Monterey Jack and Baby Spinach
description: This one-and-done dinner-in-a-hurry packs Beyond Meat®, veggies and pasta into one easy bowl. The best part? It's a meal everyone is sure to devour.
